WEBVTT

00:00:01.234 --> 00:00:02.620
You just turned and walked away.

00:00:06.406 --> 00:00:08.841
You just turned and walked away like that.

00:00:12.512 --> 00:00:14.847
I finally found you.

00:00:15.682 --> 00:00:18.183
I won't let go ever again.

00:00:19.386 --> 00:00:21.086
He Xiang Yong.

00:00:41.408 --> 00:00:43.409
You have the wrong person.

00:00:49.282 --> 00:00:51.418
No, I don't.

00:00:51.418 --> 00:00:53.186
I can feel it.

00:00:53.186 --> 00:00:55.288
You are He Xiang Yong.

00:00:56.156 --> 00:00:58.190
You are He Xiang Yong.

00:01:01.695 --> 00:01:03.758
Fine.

00:01:03.758 --> 00:01:05.865
I'm just as pathetic as him.

00:01:05.865 --> 00:01:07.400
Just as useless.

00:01:07.400 --> 00:01:09.803
We can't do anything right.

00:01:09.803 --> 00:01:11.838
We just drag others down.

00:01:11.838 --> 00:01:13.739
- Making others clean up our messes.
- Don't say that.

00:01:13.739 --> 00:01:15.941
- Holding everyone back.
- Don't say that.

00:01:15.941 --> 00:01:17.810
Listen to me.

00:01:19.312 --> 00:01:22.348
Listen to me.

00:01:23.984 --> 00:01:25.505
I'm telling you,

00:01:26.653 --> 00:01:29.221
only you understand how I feel.

00:01:30.857 --> 00:01:34.060
You gave me the best birthday gift ever.

00:01:34.060 --> 00:01:36.662
- That sea turtle drawing...
- Shut up.

00:01:41.968 --> 00:01:44.504
You have no right to mention that drawing.

00:01:45.672 --> 00:01:47.006
I...

00:01:49.375 --> 00:01:52.278
He's just like that drawing.

00:01:52.278 --> 00:01:54.314
He's already been torn to pieces.

00:01:54.314 --> 00:01:56.082
He's broken.

00:01:56.916 --> 00:01:58.518
Do you understand?

00:02:04.424 --> 00:02:06.091
I'm sorry.

00:02:07.927 --> 00:02:10.563
I should have protected you back then.

00:02:11.464 --> 00:02:13.365
It's my fault.

00:02:14.734 --> 00:02:16.303
- I'm so sorry.
- Chen Hao Wei.

00:02:16.303 --> 00:02:18.838
- I'm sorry.
- Chen Hao Wei.

00:02:20.540 --> 00:02:22.808
Don't tell me these things now.

00:02:25.111 --> 00:02:28.044
I'm in no mood to think about all that.

00:02:32.118 --> 00:02:34.887
I've already faced reality.

00:02:37.157 --> 00:02:39.291
The whole world hates me.

00:02:40.693 --> 00:02:42.595
No one likes me.

00:02:48.902 --> 00:02:51.170
Thank you very much.

00:02:57.550 --> 00:02:59.870
♫ ♫

00:02:59.870 --> 00:03:03.083
♫ ♫

00:03:03.083 --> 00:03:05.051
But I like you.

00:03:05.718 --> 00:03:07.353
He Xiang Yong.

00:03:10.730 --> 00:03:16.810
♫ ♫

00:03:16.810 --> 00:03:24.360
♫ ♫

00:03:25.430 --> 00:03:28.790
♫ ♫

00:03:28.790 --> 00:03:32.490
♫ ♫

00:03:34.614 --> 00:03:37.016
Are you crazy, Chen Hao Wei?

00:03:38.940 --> 00:03:43.156
♫ ♫

00:03:43.156 --> 00:03:44.559
Yes.

00:03:46.626 --> 00:03:48.295
I am crazy.

00:03:49.496 --> 00:03:52.360
I've gone crazy looking for you.

00:03:52.360 --> 00:03:55.160
♫ ♫

00:03:55.160 --> 00:03:58.020
I'm crazily in love with you.

00:03:58.020 --> 00:04:01.141
♫ ♫

00:04:01.141 --> 00:04:03.542
Do you dare to go crazy with me?

00:04:05.580 --> 00:04:09.015
♫ ♫

00:04:09.015 --> 00:04:10.917
He Xiang Yong.

00:04:10.917 --> 00:04:12.152
Chen Hao Wei, let me go.

00:04:12.152 --> 00:04:13.152
He Xiang Yong.

00:04:13.152 --> 00:04:15.121
Don't disappear again.

00:04:15.121 --> 00:04:17.390
Let me go.

00:04:17.390 --> 00:04:18.959
Chen Hao Wei.

00:04:18.959 --> 00:04:20.226
Let me go.

00:04:20.226 --> 00:04:22.260
You...

00:04:22.260 --> 00:04:24.731
Let go of me!

00:04:24.731 --> 00:04:26.599
Let me go.

00:04:29.430 --> 00:04:32.910
♫ ♫

00:04:32.910 --> 00:04:37.030
♫ ♫

00:04:37.030 --> 00:04:40.080
♫ ♫

00:04:42.130 --> 00:04:49.360
Timing and Subtitles brought to you by
7️⃣Shooting Stars Team @Viki.com

00:04:49.360 --> 00:04:52.590
♫ ♫

00:04:52.590 --> 00:04:56.540
♫ ♫

00:04:56.540 --> 00:05:00.660
♫ ♫

00:05:00.660 --> 00:05:06.530
♫ ♫

00:05:06.530 --> 00:05:10.760
♫ ♫

00:05:14.530 --> 00:05:17.660
♫ ♫

00:05:22.189 --> 00:05:24.324
- Where's He Xiang Yong?

00:05:24.324 --> 00:05:25.758
We're here.

00:05:26.592 --> 00:05:29.195
Drink more...

00:05:31.399 --> 00:05:33.599
We're back. Get some rest.

00:05:33.599 --> 00:05:35.268
I'm going home now.

00:05:35.268 --> 00:05:38.204
No, you can't leave.

00:05:39.872 --> 00:05:41.674
Are you a koala?

00:05:41.674 --> 00:05:43.176
I am.

00:05:43.176 --> 00:05:44.679
I am...

00:05:44.679 --> 00:05:46.679
the Big Bad Wolf.

00:05:47.880 --> 00:05:49.415
Then...

00:05:49.415 --> 00:05:51.050
I'm Little Red Riding Hood.

00:05:51.050 --> 00:05:53.386
No, you're not.

00:05:53.386 --> 00:05:56.622
You're a gift that fell from a shooting star.

00:05:56.622 --> 00:05:58.858
A gift that landed right on me.

00:06:02.495 --> 00:06:04.831
Are you sure you won't let me go?

00:06:04.831 --> 00:06:06.866
Don't you like me?

00:06:06.866 --> 00:06:09.238
If you like me, why are you leaving?

00:06:13.639 --> 00:06:15.875
It's so warm.

00:06:15.875 --> 00:06:17.810
I'm so happy.

00:06:18.511 --> 00:06:22.282
If only we could stay together
like this every day.

00:06:25.752 --> 00:06:27.586
Won't you regret this?

00:06:28.688 --> 00:06:30.422
I don't know.

00:06:41.200 --> 00:06:43.402
I'm afraid I'll lose control.

00:06:58.117 --> 00:07:00.589
This way, you won't lose control.

00:07:03.122 --> 00:07:04.791
I can't take it anymore.

00:07:04.791 --> 00:07:06.859
Can't take what?

00:07:13.065 --> 00:07:14.833
It tickles!

00:08:33.746 --> 00:08:35.114
Wait a minute.

00:08:36.816 --> 00:08:38.517
What are you doing?

00:08:39.685 --> 00:08:41.954
You've kissed me all over like this,

00:08:41.954 --> 00:08:43.989
and you're asking what I'm doing?

00:08:45.024 --> 00:08:47.292
No, not now.

00:08:50.663 --> 00:08:52.331
Next time.

00:08:59.972 --> 00:09:00.973
Li Wan Zhe.

00:09:00.973 --> 00:09:03.842
Dudu, stop messing with me.

00:09:12.151 --> 00:09:14.720
He really can't hold his liquor.

00:09:44.050 --> 00:09:46.352
Get the alarm, please.

00:09:46.352 --> 00:09:48.654
Chen Hao Wei.

00:10:00.933 --> 00:10:03.902
How did we get back to the inn yesterday?

00:10:17.283 --> 00:10:18.851
Oh, right.

00:10:20.319 --> 00:10:22.654
Did I bring you back?

00:10:24.890 --> 00:10:26.559
You brought me back?

00:10:26.559 --> 00:10:28.894
More like I brought you back.

00:10:29.729 --> 00:10:31.630
Whatever.

00:10:33.966 --> 00:10:35.935
I'm so thirsty.

00:10:35.935 --> 00:10:38.403
Rock-paper-scissors. Loser gets the water.

00:10:39.271 --> 00:10:41.707
Rock, paper, scissors!

00:10:41.707 --> 00:10:44.610
I've prepared fish soup and tea for you.

00:10:44.610 --> 00:10:46.579
It's to help you sober up.

00:10:46.579 --> 00:10:49.482
Don't leave a single drop.

00:10:49.482 --> 00:10:51.850
You're both as bad as each other.

00:10:58.090 --> 00:10:59.691
Mr. He.

00:11:00.559 --> 00:11:01.760
The two of us...

00:11:01.760 --> 00:11:04.530
We didn't cause any trouble yesterday, did we?

00:11:06.132 --> 00:11:07.734
Why don't you take a guess?

00:11:07.734 --> 00:11:09.568
Troublemaker No. 2.

00:11:14.674 --> 00:11:15.708
I'll show you how I walk.

00:11:15.708 --> 00:11:17.009
You're straying farther and farther away.

00:11:17.009 --> 00:11:18.777
It's dangerous.

00:11:19.745 --> 00:11:21.113
What's that?

00:11:21.113 --> 00:11:23.549
Huh? What do you see?

00:11:23.549 --> 00:11:25.885
Why are there two people up ahead?

00:11:25.885 --> 00:11:28.688
- Who are they?
- Why are they collapsed here?

00:11:29.789 --> 00:11:31.657
Hang on.

00:11:31.657 --> 00:11:33.125
Go this way.

00:11:34.226 --> 00:11:35.627
Don't throw up.

00:11:37.730 --> 00:11:40.366
- What's going on?
- How did you end up vomiting like this?

00:11:40.366 --> 00:11:41.434
My clothes!

00:11:41.434 --> 00:11:43.335
My clothes are ruined!

00:11:43.335 --> 00:11:45.905
You'll have to pay for the dry cleaning.

00:11:45.905 --> 00:11:47.472
Walk slowly.

00:11:50.443 --> 00:11:52.978
Anyway, that was what happened.

00:11:52.978 --> 00:11:55.881
And you said you'd take care of him.

00:11:57.850 --> 00:12:00.019
Mr. He, I'm sorry.

00:12:00.019 --> 00:12:02.821
Next time, we won't drink so much again.

00:12:04.924 --> 00:12:06.792
Forget it.

00:12:06.792 --> 00:12:09.728
I suppose everyone hasn't been
in a good mood lately.

00:12:10.329 --> 00:12:11.430
Finish your fish congee,

00:12:11.430 --> 00:12:13.065
and get ready to work.

00:12:13.065 --> 00:12:14.833
I'm going fishing.

00:12:21.540 --> 00:12:23.308
Thanks, Mr. He.

00:12:49.301 --> 00:12:52.337
Um... Last night...

00:12:53.739 --> 00:12:55.607
Last night...

00:12:56.942 --> 00:12:59.478
Well... You...

00:13:00.646 --> 00:13:01.747
I...

00:13:03.108 --> 00:13:04.461
We...

00:13:05.494 --> 00:13:07.085
We...

00:13:09.255 --> 00:13:10.456
Never mind.

00:13:10.456 --> 00:13:11.456
I mean...

00:13:11.456 --> 00:13:13.159
We were lucky last night.

00:13:13.159 --> 00:13:15.027
We didn't get run over by a car.

00:13:17.630 --> 00:13:21.066
Speaking of which, my body feels like...

00:13:21.066 --> 00:13:22.968
it's been hit by a train.

00:13:22.968 --> 00:13:25.103
I'm sore all over.

00:13:59.471 --> 00:14:02.308
Angela, you're totally fine.

00:14:02.308 --> 00:14:03.508
Really?

00:14:04.210 --> 00:14:05.311
But I just feel like...

00:14:05.311 --> 00:14:06.678
You know?

00:14:09.381 --> 00:14:10.716
Something feels off here.

00:14:10.716 --> 00:14:11.784
Listen to it for me again.

00:14:11.784 --> 00:14:13.719
I just checked. It's normal.

00:14:13.719 --> 00:14:14.820
Look, your complexion is great,

00:14:14.820 --> 00:14:16.254
and you're full of energy.

00:14:17.189 --> 00:14:18.424
All right.

00:14:18.424 --> 00:14:19.925
I guess I'm fine, too.

00:14:21.227 --> 00:14:22.427
Lend me that for a second.

00:14:23.028 --> 00:14:24.663
Let me see if you're okay.

00:14:24.663 --> 00:14:27.165
What could be wrong with me?

00:14:30.202 --> 00:14:32.504
All right, you seem fine, too.

00:14:35.042 --> 00:14:36.876
Old He is the one with a problem.

00:14:36.876 --> 00:14:39.378
What's wrong with Old He?

00:14:39.378 --> 00:14:40.846
Old He...

00:14:40.846 --> 00:14:42.667
What could be wrong with him?

00:14:45.217 --> 00:14:47.994
Then why is he selling the inn?

00:15:21.086 --> 00:15:22.813
I'm sorry.

00:15:25.357 --> 00:15:27.993
I didn't take good care of this home.

00:15:35.101 --> 00:15:36.101
Where's the tape?

00:15:36.101 --> 00:15:38.437
Didn't I tell you to find tape?

00:15:39.371 --> 00:15:41.039
I can't find it.

00:15:44.310 --> 00:15:46.478
Then take those...

00:15:47.079 --> 00:15:48.447
those maps of the inn,

00:15:48.447 --> 00:15:49.915
and the photo frames.

00:15:49.915 --> 00:15:51.617
Organize everything that can be recycled.

00:15:51.617 --> 00:15:54.153
Find a place to recycle them.

00:15:54.153 --> 00:15:55.323
Wait, no.

00:15:55.323 --> 00:15:56.355
You haven't even signed the contract yet.

00:15:56.355 --> 00:15:57.690
Why are you in such a hurry to pack?

00:15:57.690 --> 00:15:59.858
It has to be done sooner or later, right?

00:15:59.858 --> 00:16:01.060
Hurry up. Pack everything up.

00:16:01.060 --> 00:16:02.561
Get it done.

00:16:03.963 --> 00:16:05.965
What about the guest book?

00:16:05.965 --> 00:16:07.899
Are you throwing that out too?

00:16:11.704 --> 00:16:14.206
Xiang Yong bought that guest book.

00:16:15.107 --> 00:16:16.875
I'll wait for him to return and decide.

00:16:19.044 --> 00:16:20.679
Old He!

00:16:20.679 --> 00:16:22.180
Old He!

00:16:22.915 --> 00:16:26.451
Come here! We have guests!

00:16:27.186 --> 00:16:28.687
Old He!

00:16:30.089 --> 00:16:32.925
You don't have to sell the inn anymore.

00:16:32.925 --> 00:16:35.060
Look at this.

00:16:35.761 --> 00:16:38.497
Village Chief Wang donated 20,000 alone.

00:16:38.497 --> 00:16:41.367
And I just ran into someone outside.

00:16:41.367 --> 00:16:42.634
De from the grocery store.

00:16:42.634 --> 00:16:45.571
He gave all of yesterday's earnings.

00:16:45.571 --> 00:16:46.572
And Madam Jiao...

00:16:46.572 --> 00:16:49.174
She doesn't know how to use an ATM,

00:16:49.174 --> 00:16:50.609
so she rushed home

00:16:50.609 --> 00:16:52.344
and brought out her dowry.

00:16:52.344 --> 00:16:54.813
There's Jin Fa's, and Chun Hua's.

00:16:54.813 --> 00:16:56.048
They all donated.

00:16:56.048 --> 00:16:57.282
Hua, what about yours?

00:16:57.282 --> 00:16:59.184
Mine is already in there.

00:17:00.252 --> 00:17:02.287
This is from all of us.

00:17:03.255 --> 00:17:05.024
Thank you.

00:17:05.024 --> 00:17:06.759
But this isn't enough.

00:17:06.759 --> 00:17:08.660
Take it back.

00:17:17.469 --> 00:17:18.804
Plus this check of mine.

00:17:18.804 --> 00:17:19.872
Five million.

00:17:19.872 --> 00:17:21.573
That should be enough.

00:17:26.445 --> 00:17:28.714
I can't accept this.

00:17:28.714 --> 00:17:31.116
This is everyone's hard-earned money.

00:17:31.116 --> 00:17:32.851
Especially you.

00:17:32.851 --> 00:17:34.887
You worked so hard to raise Wan Zhe alone.

00:17:34.887 --> 00:17:36.922
This is your hard-earned retirement fund.

00:17:36.922 --> 00:17:37.990
Keep it for your retirement.

00:17:37.990 --> 00:17:39.658
Don't give it to me.

00:17:39.658 --> 00:17:41.960
Don't be silly.

00:17:41.960 --> 00:17:43.328
Back then, you and your wife

00:17:43.328 --> 00:17:45.664
helped me look after Wan Zhe every day.

00:17:45.664 --> 00:17:48.300
Listen, take this money.

00:17:48.300 --> 00:17:49.301
What for?

00:17:49.301 --> 00:17:51.770
I'm not giving it to you for free.

00:17:51.770 --> 00:17:53.572
I'm lending it to you.

00:17:53.572 --> 00:17:56.408
Let's be clear from the start.

00:17:56.408 --> 00:17:58.043
You have to write an IOU.

00:17:58.043 --> 00:18:00.012
And interest will be charged accordingly.

00:18:00.012 --> 00:18:01.013
Hey, Xiao You.

00:18:01.013 --> 00:18:02.481
Bring me that ink pad.

00:18:02.481 --> 00:18:04.249
- Here.
- That's right.

00:18:04.249 --> 00:18:06.618
Old He, don't be so stubborn.

00:18:06.618 --> 00:18:09.321
You know this inn holds
shared memories for all of us.

00:18:10.122 --> 00:18:12.524
For Starry Islet, and for Xiang Yong.

00:18:12.524 --> 00:18:14.192
Just accept it.

00:18:14.860 --> 00:18:16.728
Accept it. Come on.

00:18:20.766 --> 00:18:22.300
What's the matter now?

00:18:23.535 --> 00:18:26.505
You'd rather sell this inn
to a complete stranger

00:18:26.505 --> 00:18:29.208
than owe me money?

00:18:29.208 --> 00:18:30.544
Are you looking down on me?

00:18:30.544 --> 00:18:31.643
- Do you think I'm a joke?
- That's not what I meant.

00:18:31.643 --> 00:18:33.278
No, it's not that.

00:18:37.416 --> 00:18:38.650
I'd owe you such a huge favor.

00:18:38.650 --> 00:18:40.952
I wouldn't know how to repay you.

00:18:42.955 --> 00:18:44.189
How?

00:18:44.189 --> 00:18:47.126
By working hard to pay me back!

00:18:47.126 --> 00:18:48.560
If you ever refuse to pay,

00:18:48.560 --> 00:18:52.131
I'll tear this whole place down.

00:18:52.131 --> 00:18:53.565
Then I'll bring dogs to pee here every day.

00:18:53.565 --> 00:18:55.767
And those flowers your wife planted...

00:18:55.767 --> 00:18:57.202
I'll throw them all away.

00:18:57.202 --> 00:18:59.004
- No!
- You can't do that!

00:19:02.774 --> 00:19:04.309
I'll help pay it back.

00:19:04.943 --> 00:19:06.511
What does this have to do with you?

00:19:07.212 --> 00:19:08.713
I'm your son...

00:19:09.848 --> 00:19:12.417
I'm your son's friend, and I'm your employee.

00:19:12.417 --> 00:19:14.119
I want to do my part, too.

00:19:16.588 --> 00:19:18.290
That's the spirit!

00:19:18.290 --> 00:19:19.992
Wonderful.

00:19:19.992 --> 00:19:20.993
You're lucky.

00:19:20.993 --> 00:19:23.395
Your employee is so loyal.

00:19:25.130 --> 00:19:27.032
All right, it's settled.

00:19:27.032 --> 00:19:28.534
Let's go fishing.

00:19:28.534 --> 00:19:29.534
No, you go ahead.

00:19:29.534 --> 00:19:31.270
I already went this morning.

00:19:31.270 --> 00:19:32.738
I'm going to throw up.

00:19:32.738 --> 00:19:33.805
I told you not to drink so much.

00:19:33.805 --> 00:19:34.840
Feeling nauseous now?

00:19:34.840 --> 00:19:36.841
You drank way too much.

00:19:38.010 --> 00:19:40.345
It's your cheesiness making me sick.

00:19:40.345 --> 00:19:42.281
You guys put that money away.

00:19:42.281 --> 00:19:43.882
I'm going to open the shop. Bye.

00:19:43.882 --> 00:19:45.150
Don't just stand there.

00:19:45.150 --> 00:19:46.150
Get out of my way.

00:19:46.150 --> 00:19:48.186
So annoying. Seriously.

00:20:12.411 --> 00:20:14.313
One more.

00:20:14.313 --> 00:20:16.047
Come on.

00:20:20.652 --> 00:20:22.287
Why are you so quiet?

00:20:22.287 --> 00:20:23.655
You came fishing with me,

00:20:23.655 --> 00:20:25.824
so you must have something to talk about.

00:20:29.328 --> 00:20:32.598
Mr. Hua, why are you setting out
these paper boats?

00:20:32.598 --> 00:20:35.066
To say hi to the little dolphin.

00:20:36.068 --> 00:20:37.302
Dolphin?

00:20:38.670 --> 00:20:41.906
When I was a resident doctor
on the main island,

00:20:42.708 --> 00:20:45.477
there was a young patient.

00:20:45.477 --> 00:20:48.346
He'd been in and out of the hospital
since he was little.

00:20:49.481 --> 00:20:52.117
He really envied marine creatures.

00:20:52.718 --> 00:20:54.786
They could swim and play anywhere.

00:20:56.888 --> 00:21:00.192
He even wanted to be a little dolphin.

00:21:00.192 --> 00:21:02.961
That way, he wouldn't have to
take medicine or get shots in the sea.

00:21:03.795 --> 00:21:07.332
I jokingly told him, "Okay."

00:21:07.332 --> 00:21:09.601
"Then I'll definitely take a boat to find you."

00:21:21.380 --> 00:21:23.482
So, these paper boats

00:21:23.482 --> 00:21:25.683
hold such memories for you.

00:21:30.122 --> 00:21:32.758
I wasn't mature enough back then.

00:21:32.758 --> 00:21:35.660
I wasn't strong enough to defend
what I thought was right.

00:21:36.728 --> 00:21:39.697
That's why I caused irreparable harm.

00:21:42.834 --> 00:21:47.806
So, I've stayed on Starry Islet until now.

00:21:55.647 --> 00:21:57.715
What? Does that disappoint you?

00:21:58.583 --> 00:21:59.618
I'm not like Albert Schweitzer,

00:21:59.618 --> 00:22:01.786
with the ambition to save the world.

00:22:02.487 --> 00:22:04.889
Instead, it's more like...

00:22:05.857 --> 00:22:08.126
a story of a coward on the run.

00:22:14.466 --> 00:22:16.168
Everyone has their own memories.

00:22:16.168 --> 00:22:18.603
I have no right to judge.

00:22:20.839 --> 00:22:22.207
But...

00:22:23.775 --> 00:22:26.211
I think I saw my old self just now.

00:22:29.915 --> 00:22:31.850
If I had...

00:22:32.518 --> 00:22:33.550
a little more courage back then

00:22:33.550 --> 00:22:35.786
to protect the most important person to me,

00:22:37.122 --> 00:22:39.891
things probably wouldn't have
become as complicated as they are now.

00:22:42.894 --> 00:22:44.596
What's wrong?

00:22:44.596 --> 00:22:46.497
What kind of trouble are you in?

00:22:48.400 --> 00:22:52.938
Anyway, the beginning
of the dream is quite blurry.

00:22:52.938 --> 00:22:54.306
I only remember...

00:22:54.306 --> 00:22:57.909
The last thing I remember is
that handsome guy kissing that loser.

00:22:57.909 --> 00:22:59.744
That was when I woke up.

00:23:00.946 --> 00:23:03.014
So, you and Chen Hao Wei kissed last night?

00:23:03.014 --> 00:23:04.149
I never said that!

00:23:04.149 --> 00:23:05.183
Don't even try to deny it.

00:23:05.183 --> 00:23:06.385
I've known you for how long now?

00:23:06.385 --> 00:23:08.219
Just tell me who made the first move.

00:23:09.988 --> 00:23:11.589
It was me.

00:23:12.657 --> 00:23:13.959
How did Xiao You react?

00:23:13.959 --> 00:23:19.465
I think I might have pushed him away.

00:23:20.266 --> 00:23:21.333
I've forgotten everything else.

00:23:21.333 --> 00:23:23.568
I told you, I only remember the kissing part.

00:23:25.804 --> 00:23:27.806
Could he have just gone crazy from the alcohol?

00:23:27.806 --> 00:23:29.574
Like, trying to blackmail me or something?

00:23:30.409 --> 00:23:31.743
No way.

00:23:31.743 --> 00:23:34.646
Is Chen Hao Wei really the type
to be such a beast in disguise?

00:23:34.646 --> 00:23:35.847
True.

00:23:35.847 --> 00:23:37.749
He's not that kind of person.

00:23:39.317 --> 00:23:42.120
He must have confessed his love while drunk.

00:23:43.488 --> 00:23:45.157
Are you talking about me? Or Zhong Xiao You?

00:23:45.157 --> 00:23:47.358
I admit I have feelings for Xiao You.

00:23:48.460 --> 00:23:50.328
I think I've fallen for him.

00:23:53.665 --> 00:23:55.700
If you like him, then confess.

00:23:55.700 --> 00:23:57.635
What are you so worried about?

00:23:58.270 --> 00:23:59.571
But...

00:23:59.571 --> 00:24:01.306
I like Xiao You...

00:24:01.306 --> 00:24:03.675
because I think he's He Xiang Yong.

00:24:05.911 --> 00:24:08.479
The name I kept calling out last night...

00:24:09.247 --> 00:24:10.848
was He Xiang Yong.

00:24:12.150 --> 00:24:15.020
So, he doesn't remember kissing you at all?

00:24:15.020 --> 00:24:16.421
Yeah.

00:24:16.421 --> 00:24:17.589
The vibe he gave me this morning...

00:24:17.589 --> 00:24:19.357
was that he'd forgotten everything.

00:24:19.357 --> 00:24:20.792
But if it's really like you said,

00:24:20.792 --> 00:24:22.227
and the one he likes is Xiao You,

00:24:22.227 --> 00:24:23.728
how could he possibly forget?

00:24:24.329 --> 00:24:26.865
Or did he mistake Xiao You for you?

00:24:26.865 --> 00:24:28.833
So, he's playing dumb
because he's afraid to admit it.

00:24:29.468 --> 00:24:31.035
What a jerk.

00:24:31.703 --> 00:24:34.939
That's why it's even more impossible for me
to be honest with Xiao You.

00:24:36.808 --> 00:24:38.810
Because I know very well...

00:24:38.810 --> 00:24:41.012
that they aren't the same person.

00:24:41.012 --> 00:24:43.915
Even though I was confused for a while,
the truth is...

00:24:46.184 --> 00:24:48.319
the one in my heart is Xiang Yong.

00:24:49.421 --> 00:24:52.090
I can't use Xiao You as his substitute.

00:24:52.090 --> 00:24:53.123
Well, since that's the case...

00:24:53.123 --> 00:24:55.627
I think you should stick to your guns.

00:24:55.627 --> 00:24:58.597
You shouldn't start this relationship
based on a mistake.

00:24:58.597 --> 00:25:00.165
Otherwise, in the end,

00:25:00.165 --> 00:25:02.767
Xiao You will end up getting very hurt.

00:25:03.435 --> 00:25:04.536
Wait, that's not right.

00:25:04.536 --> 00:25:06.371
Whether you're Zhong Xiao You or He Xiang Yong,

00:25:06.371 --> 00:25:07.739
you're still you.

00:25:07.739 --> 00:25:09.374
It's like shaved ice and snow ice.

00:25:09.374 --> 00:25:11.209
They're just different names
for the same thing.

00:25:13.678 --> 00:25:16.647
I can't believe you came up
with such twisted logic.

00:25:18.483 --> 00:25:20.918
But it actually makes sense.

00:25:26.925 --> 00:25:28.193
If you put it that way,

00:25:28.193 --> 00:25:30.529
Chen Hao Wei has always been
consistently devoted to you.

00:25:30.529 --> 00:25:32.630
That's so romantic.

00:25:33.732 --> 00:25:34.966
Are you going to accept him?

00:25:36.167 --> 00:25:37.902
Accept what?

00:25:38.637 --> 00:25:40.505
And as who?

00:25:40.505 --> 00:25:42.407
As me?

00:25:42.407 --> 00:25:43.808
Or as Zhong Xiao You?

00:25:45.010 --> 00:25:48.613
Besides, I have nothing left to tear apart.

00:25:49.915 --> 00:25:52.717
Bro, say something I can understand for once.

00:25:59.057 --> 00:26:01.092
But look.

00:26:01.092 --> 00:26:02.661
My wish came true so easily.

00:26:02.661 --> 00:26:06.397
Don't you think it feels a bit surreal?

00:26:07.699 --> 00:26:08.934
It's like...

00:26:08.934 --> 00:26:11.102
if you found a million dollars
on the street today,

00:26:11.102 --> 00:26:12.370
and brought it home,

00:26:12.971 --> 00:26:14.672
would you really be happy?

00:26:21.980 --> 00:26:23.581
Li Wan Zhe!

00:26:25.617 --> 00:26:28.086
Hama-chan! Don't you have to
go out to sea today?

00:26:28.086 --> 00:26:29.521
I quit.

00:26:29.521 --> 00:26:30.889
Huh?

00:26:30.889 --> 00:26:32.691
I'm going to work here from now on.

00:26:32.691 --> 00:26:34.358
I'll be in your care.

00:27:05.924 --> 00:27:06.992
Tell me.

00:27:06.992 --> 00:27:08.393
Why did you quit?

00:27:08.393 --> 00:27:09.794
Did something happen?

00:27:09.794 --> 00:27:11.329
Or did Zhong bully you?

00:27:12.597 --> 00:27:14.933
Your face looks so funny.

00:27:14.933 --> 00:27:17.035
You look just like Zhong.

00:27:17.035 --> 00:27:18.403
Hamaguchi Aomi!

00:27:18.403 --> 00:27:21.005
I'm being serious right now.

00:27:24.509 --> 00:27:26.177
Don't worry.

00:27:26.878 --> 00:27:28.480
Nothing happened.

00:27:28.480 --> 00:27:30.581
And no one bullied me.

00:27:31.916 --> 00:27:33.685
I quit...

00:27:33.685 --> 00:27:35.553
because of you.

00:27:35.553 --> 00:27:36.855
Me?

00:27:36.855 --> 00:27:37.889
Yeah.

00:27:37.889 --> 00:27:38.890
You told me last night

00:27:38.890 --> 00:27:41.960
that you wanted to hang out
with me every day.

00:27:41.960 --> 00:27:46.598
So, I quit my job to be with you every day.

00:27:46.598 --> 00:27:48.986
When did I say that?

00:27:48.986 --> 00:27:50.287
Have you forgotten?

00:27:52.504 --> 00:27:54.405
Let me help you remember.

00:27:57.575 --> 00:28:00.178
You hugged me like this and said...

00:28:01.813 --> 00:28:03.448
"I'm so happy."

00:28:03.448 --> 00:28:05.316
"It's so warm."

00:28:05.316 --> 00:28:08.553
"If only we could be like this
and hang out every day."

00:28:10.321 --> 00:28:11.489
What do you think?

00:28:11.489 --> 00:28:13.591
Does it feel familiar?

00:28:14.626 --> 00:28:15.694
People talk nonsense when they're drunk.

00:28:15.694 --> 00:28:17.528
How could you take it seriously?

00:28:18.396 --> 00:28:20.198
I told you.

00:28:20.832 --> 00:28:24.135
As long as it's about you, I'll give it my all.

00:28:26.337 --> 00:28:27.806
But...

00:28:27.806 --> 00:28:29.474
you used to say

00:28:29.474 --> 00:28:31.076
that being a sailor was your dream.

00:28:31.076 --> 00:28:32.877
You said you wanted to travel the world.

00:28:44.622 --> 00:28:46.157
From now on,

00:28:46.958 --> 00:28:48.993
you are my dream.

00:28:48.993 --> 00:28:51.262
You are my whole world.

00:28:52.397 --> 00:28:55.499
Boss, I'm going to work now.

00:29:29.601 --> 00:29:31.769
What do you want to write? I'll do it.

00:29:33.138 --> 00:29:34.305
Okay, just write the words.

00:29:34.305 --> 00:29:35.740
Don't draw anything.

00:29:35.740 --> 00:29:38.342
I'm saving the drawing
for when Xiang Yong comes back.

00:29:46.151 --> 00:29:49.921
He caused such a mess
and then suddenly disappeared.

00:29:49.921 --> 00:29:51.189
Aren't you mad at him?

00:29:51.189 --> 00:29:52.990
You're still doing so much for him.

00:29:54.492 --> 00:29:56.060
I am mad.

00:29:56.060 --> 00:29:58.729
I'm mad that I didn't teach him
how to box when he was little.

00:29:59.864 --> 00:30:02.267
Now when he's mistreated,

00:30:02.267 --> 00:30:05.569
he just takes it and won't fight back.

00:30:08.807 --> 00:30:10.942
But are you worried about him?

00:30:10.942 --> 00:30:13.544
Aren't you afraid he won't come back?

00:30:20.385 --> 00:30:22.553
Of course I'm worried.

00:30:25.857 --> 00:30:28.660
But he has his own thoughts.

00:30:28.660 --> 00:30:31.329
Anyway, his home and dad are here.

00:30:31.329 --> 00:30:34.098
He can come back whenever he wants.

00:30:38.102 --> 00:30:41.973
If he knew that you almost sold the inn

00:30:41.973 --> 00:30:44.142
because of him,

00:30:44.142 --> 00:30:48.279
he'd drink with me for three days straight.

00:30:48.279 --> 00:30:51.515
- He'd cry and say he was immature.
- That's really heavy.

00:30:52.884 --> 00:30:53.885
So heavy...

00:30:53.885 --> 00:30:56.387
That rascal doesn't even know how to drink.

00:30:57.322 --> 00:30:58.989
Didn't you know?

00:31:02.327 --> 00:31:05.496
His cure for a hangover is hiking.

00:31:06.397 --> 00:31:09.567
Because from the summit,
he can see the ocean...

00:31:10.201 --> 00:31:12.069
and Starry Islet.

00:31:21.379 --> 00:31:24.849
When did that rascal start drinking?

00:31:25.783 --> 00:31:27.918
After he started working.

00:31:32.924 --> 00:31:34.992
That rascal...

00:31:36.261 --> 00:31:38.829
He knows how to drink with others,

00:31:40.198 --> 00:31:43.701
but he won't have a drink with me at home.

00:31:45.904 --> 00:31:49.407
He just doesn't want you
to see his vulnerable side.

00:31:50.909 --> 00:31:53.111
When he's drunk,

00:31:53.111 --> 00:31:56.347
he's talkative, childish, and a crybaby.

00:31:56.347 --> 00:31:58.683
You'd probably find it annoying.

00:31:58.683 --> 00:32:00.184
That's nothing.

00:32:00.184 --> 00:32:02.620
He inherited that from me.

00:32:04.722 --> 00:32:09.027
Anyway, in his heart,
I'm just a bad-tempered dad...

00:32:09.027 --> 00:32:11.949
who isn't worth sharing his feelings with.

00:32:13.531 --> 00:32:15.499
Of course not.

00:32:16.634 --> 00:32:18.169
He actually knows

00:32:18.169 --> 00:32:20.638
that you only want what's best for him.

00:32:21.239 --> 00:32:22.707
It's just that...

00:32:22.707 --> 00:32:24.775
he doesn't know how to express it.

00:32:28.446 --> 00:32:30.873
Then I was right to keep that blackboard.

00:32:31.816 --> 00:32:35.586
Xiang Yong has always been sensitive.

00:32:35.586 --> 00:32:37.021
His drawings...

00:32:37.622 --> 00:32:40.057
are probably what he wants to say.

00:32:45.496 --> 00:32:48.466
By the way, tell him this for me.

00:32:48.466 --> 00:32:51.769
His dad only hates one kind of drinker.

00:32:51.769 --> 00:32:55.406
The kind that gets rowdy when they're drunk.

00:32:57.008 --> 00:32:58.309
Isn't that exactly like you?

00:32:59.210 --> 00:33:00.644
Damn it.

00:33:03.314 --> 00:33:06.584
When he comes back,
why don't you ask him for a drink yourself?

00:33:20.331 --> 00:33:22.367
I'm the chef today.

00:33:22.367 --> 00:33:23.968
I'll make some snacks to go with the drinks.

00:33:23.968 --> 00:33:25.336
And your favorite garlic shrimp rice noodles.

00:33:25.336 --> 00:33:26.604
You know how to make that?

00:33:26.604 --> 00:33:27.605
I do.

00:33:27.605 --> 00:33:29.707
That's Xiang Yong's mom's secret recipe.

00:33:29.707 --> 00:33:31.409
You can make it?

00:33:31.409 --> 00:33:33.144
He taught me.

00:33:33.144 --> 00:33:34.812
You won't be able to pull it off.
But you're in luck.

00:33:34.812 --> 00:33:36.347
I can. I'll cook it for you.

00:33:36.347 --> 00:33:37.782
I can do it, don't worry.

00:33:37.782 --> 00:33:40.151
I'm very confident, okay?

00:33:40.151 --> 00:33:42.019
Young man...

00:33:42.687 --> 00:33:46.324
I'm starting to wonder...
What exactly is your relationship with my son?

00:33:46.324 --> 00:33:47.358
We're just good friends.

00:33:47.358 --> 00:33:48.994
The kind who tell each other everything.

00:33:48.994 --> 00:33:50.061
No, wait.

00:33:50.061 --> 00:33:51.696
He even taught you this?

00:33:51.696 --> 00:33:53.297
You know how to make it too?

00:33:55.933 --> 00:33:57.201
Are you sure you know how to cook it?

00:33:57.201 --> 00:33:59.003
It'll be fine.

00:33:59.003 --> 00:34:00.504
Is the oil hot enough?

00:34:01.172 --> 00:34:03.141
Wait a bit longer.

00:34:03.141 --> 00:34:05.076
- Wait a bit longer?
- It's about ready.

00:34:05.076 --> 00:34:07.811
The shrimp and...

00:34:08.613 --> 00:34:10.247
The glass noodles.

00:34:11.582 --> 00:34:12.717
The oil can't be too hot.

00:34:12.717 --> 00:34:14.352
The garlic will burn instantly, you know?

00:34:14.352 --> 00:34:16.988
I know. Let it sauté for a bit.

00:34:16.988 --> 00:34:18.020
It doesn't need to sauté for long.

00:34:18.020 --> 00:34:19.090
Hurry up and add the chili!

00:34:19.090 --> 00:34:20.992
- Hurry up!
- It's fine.

00:34:20.992 --> 00:34:22.527
This is how I always did it, okay?

00:34:22.527 --> 00:34:24.362
This isn't right.

00:34:24.362 --> 00:34:26.664
Don't worry, it'll work.

00:34:27.765 --> 00:34:29.534
I can't watch this. Here, let me through.

00:34:29.534 --> 00:34:31.636
Please. Go stand over there.

00:34:31.636 --> 00:34:34.172
I said I'm cooking today.

00:34:34.172 --> 00:34:35.740
Go help me taste the sauce, okay?

00:34:35.740 --> 00:34:37.942
Please. Thank you.

00:34:55.927 --> 00:34:58.362
It's not bad.

00:34:58.362 --> 00:34:59.564
You need to put that in quickly.

00:34:59.564 --> 00:35:01.099
Otherwise...

00:35:01.099 --> 00:35:03.067
Add water.

00:35:09.504 --> 00:35:11.780
[I hope you're doing well.
This place is truly wonderful. From Hao Wei]

00:35:25.523 --> 00:35:27.157
Chen Hao Wei.

00:35:28.659 --> 00:35:31.195
It's almost ready. We can get ready to eat.

00:35:33.164 --> 00:35:34.465
What are you doing?

00:35:44.642 --> 00:35:46.644
If you ever see He Xiang Yong,

00:35:48.346 --> 00:35:50.547
please give this to him for me.

00:35:57.655 --> 00:35:59.189
I'll go help out first.

00:36:52.605 --> 00:37:01.919
[Epilogue]

00:37:01.919 --> 00:37:03.520
Chen Hao Wei.

00:37:04.755 --> 00:37:05.890
What are you doing?

00:37:05.890 --> 00:37:07.592
Waiting for someone.

00:37:07.592 --> 00:37:09.193
Waiting for me?

00:37:09.994 --> 00:37:11.329
Just kidding.

00:37:11.329 --> 00:37:13.698
I saw you looking at a drawing just now.

00:37:13.698 --> 00:37:14.732
Yeah.

00:37:14.732 --> 00:37:16.333
Can I see it?

00:37:19.870 --> 00:37:21.905
- I'm taking it.
- Okay.

00:37:22.640 --> 00:37:24.175
It's a sea turtle.

00:37:24.175 --> 00:37:26.577
Yeah, I really like sea turtles.

00:37:28.879 --> 00:37:30.348
Did He Xiang Yong draw this?

00:37:30.348 --> 00:37:32.649
Yeah. Why?

00:37:34.685 --> 00:37:38.458
Don't you think these childish brushstrokes
are really ugly?

00:37:38.458 --> 00:37:40.894
What is this even supposed to be?

00:37:40.894 --> 00:37:42.960
No wonder you were laughing.

00:37:42.960 --> 00:37:45.165
Is this what you were laughing at?

00:37:45.165 --> 00:37:47.465
I guess so. I think it's pretty laughable.

00:37:47.465 --> 00:37:50.067
Yeah, I think so, too.

00:37:51.269 --> 00:37:55.273
You know, He Xiang Yong
is a very, very strange person.

00:37:55.273 --> 00:37:57.141
No one in our class likes him.

00:37:57.141 --> 00:37:58.576
But I think you're very kind.

00:37:58.576 --> 00:38:00.745
I mean, you still spend time being his friend,

00:38:00.745 --> 00:38:02.613
helping him with his homework and all.

00:38:02.613 --> 00:38:05.016
Well, I'm just helping a classmate.

00:38:05.016 --> 00:38:06.617
So, you also think he needs help?

00:38:06.617 --> 00:38:07.652
Then we're quite alike.

00:38:07.652 --> 00:38:11.255
We both help people
who look like they need help.

00:38:12.023 --> 00:38:15.063
Then can you do me a favor?

00:38:15.063 --> 00:38:16.094
What is it?

00:38:16.094 --> 00:38:17.795
I want to borrow this.

00:38:17.795 --> 00:38:20.430
Lend it to me. I'll return it next week.

00:38:21.300 --> 00:38:22.835
Aren't you in the art class?

00:38:22.835 --> 00:38:25.002
You should be able to draw one yourself.

00:38:30.441 --> 00:38:32.943
Class is starting. I'm heading off.

00:39:10.848 --> 00:39:12.816
Chen Hao Wei said he's very tired.

00:39:16.554 --> 00:39:17.555
You know Hao Wei.

00:39:17.555 --> 00:39:19.256
He's the most popular guy in school.

00:39:19.256 --> 00:39:20.257
He's very well-liked.

00:39:20.257 --> 00:39:22.026
Everyone loves him.

00:39:22.026 --> 00:39:24.195
So, with all the activities
and all the clubs...

00:39:24.195 --> 00:39:26.230
What are you trying to say?

00:39:29.200 --> 00:39:31.102
I'm trying to say...

00:39:31.102 --> 00:39:32.670
Hao Wei's grades have dropped.

00:39:32.670 --> 00:39:34.672
And he keeps dozing off in class.

00:39:34.672 --> 00:39:36.373
You think it's my fault?

00:39:37.174 --> 00:39:38.809
I didn't say that.

00:39:38.809 --> 00:39:41.045
Why do you think so poorly of me?

00:39:41.045 --> 00:39:42.113
I'm just speaking from the perspective

00:39:42.113 --> 00:39:44.115
of being Hao Wei's good friend.

00:39:44.115 --> 00:39:45.449
I want to offer a suggestion

00:39:45.449 --> 00:39:48.151
that will help both you and Hao Wei.

00:39:49.433 --> 00:39:52.169
Have you considered going to cram school?

00:39:54.725 --> 00:39:56.460
No need.

00:39:56.460 --> 00:39:58.929
I won't trouble Hao Wei anymore.

00:39:59.797 --> 00:40:01.965
Don't be like that.

00:40:02.933 --> 00:40:06.270
What I mean is,
I've also been inspired by Hao Wei,

00:40:06.270 --> 00:40:08.339
so I want to join him

00:40:08.339 --> 00:40:10.453
in helping students who are falling behind.

00:40:10.453 --> 00:40:13.410
Wouldn't it be great if we all worked hard
and improved together?

00:40:15.980 --> 00:40:17.648
No, thanks.

00:40:17.648 --> 00:40:18.983
I'm tired.

00:40:18.983 --> 00:40:21.051
I don't want to try anymore.

00:40:26.457 --> 00:40:28.125
He Xiang Yong.

00:40:29.393 --> 00:40:31.328
If there's anything
you need help with in the future,

00:40:31.328 --> 00:40:33.297
you can always tell me.

00:40:33.297 --> 00:40:34.898
I mean it.

00:40:42.873 --> 00:40:44.641
Just let me know.

00:41:27.151 --> 00:41:28.285
If you want to see him off,

00:41:28.285 --> 00:41:30.387
it's not too late to go to the pier now.

00:41:31.355 --> 00:41:33.057
He Xiang Yong is the one I can't let go of.

00:41:33.057 --> 00:41:35.693
The one I've always loved is He Xiang Yong.

00:41:35.693 --> 00:41:37.995
You don't need to become him for me.

00:41:39.231 --> 00:41:40.262
Li Wan Zhe.

00:41:40.262 --> 00:41:41.265
Are you hungry?

00:41:41.265 --> 00:41:43.400
You've worked hard all day.

00:41:43.400 --> 00:41:45.502
I'll make you a late-night snack.